content: Please fix your date feature from and end for texts. It's not working causing too much data and I get an error message. Please do it as soon as possible I need it for court.
replyContent: hi, you need to specify the from/to dates using the format mm/dd/yyyy or dd/mm/yyyy. if your keyboard does not have the slash key you will have to install another keyboard.

replyContent: hi, what has changed with the last update is that you have to select the email application to use for sending the SMS text before you select the specific SMS conversation. this is asked when you click on the SMS to Email button.
